## 🔹 8. Real Scenario — Error Handling

Request:

```
GET /devices
(no token)
```

Response:

```
401
```

Request:

```
GET /enumerator
user token
```

Response:

```
403
```

Request:

```
wrong URL
```

Response:

```
404
```

Automation must check all.

